&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain backend services and APIs using Python (FastAPI) that support web, mobile, and ML-driven workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain fullstack internal applications, including:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Web frontends (e.g., React)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mobile applications using React Native for operational and field workflows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and operate cloud infrastructure on GCP, including networking, compute, storage, and IAM.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage infrastructure-as-code (e.g., Terraform, Pulumi) and deployment pipelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and evolve scalable data platforms using BigQuery, Python, and Spark.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement and maintain service-oriented and event-driven architectures using Pub/Sub, Kafka, and related tooling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with ML engineers to support model deployment, orchestration, and production integration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish and maintain observability, reliability, and security across services and infrastructure (logging, metrics, alerting).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improve developer experience through better abstractions, tooling, CI/CD, and documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively identify and address scalability, performance, and operational risks across the platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree in a technical field (Computer Science, Engineering, or similar).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of experience as a Fullstack, Platform, Backend, or Infrastructure-oriented Engineer.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong backend experience with Python and frameworks such as FastAPI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience operating cloud infrastructure on GCP (preferred) or AWS.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with infrastructure-as-code, CI/CD pipelines, and production deployments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience designing and operating service-oriented and event-driven systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with messaging and streaming platforms (Pub/Sub, Kafka).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong systems thinking, with the ability to reason across product, platform, data, and infrastructure layers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working independently in a cross-functional, distributed environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear communicator who can collaborate effectively with science, ML, and automation teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to haves:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with frontend development (e.g., React) and mobile development using React Native.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Agentic workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
