&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Inventory Management&lt;/strong&gt;: Partner with cross-functional teams (e.g., finance, operations, facilities) to develop and implement an effective inventory management system for all capital expenditures (capex). Track capex assets, monitor utilization, and identify opportunities for optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
